Migration.Name: Se modifica la ventana de Notas de Entrega

Data.oldValue: The Shipment Guide Window allows you to enter and modify Shipment Guides.

PO.Data: The Shipment Note Window allows you to enter and modify Shipment Guides.

Data.oldValue: The Shipment Guide Header Tab defines the parameters of an Shipment Guide. Changing the Organization, Business Partner, Warehouse, Date Promised, etc. changes these values on all the lines.

PO.Data: The Shipment Note Header Tab defines the parameters of an Shipment Note. Changing the Organization, Business Partner, Warehouse, Date Promised, etc. changes these values on all the lines.

Data.oldValue: The Shipment Guide Line Tab defines the individual line items that comprise an Shipment Guide.

PO.Data: The Shipment Note Line Tab defines the individual line items that comprise an Shipment Note.
